reviewText: I bought this movie as a recommendation from someone and it was such a poor production.  The moral of the story is great as it stems from the bible but the acting was so so terrible.  I wouldn't watch this movie ever again, I wish I could return it!

THE PLOT THICKENS AND HAS A TWIST
WE ARE FORCED TO CONSIDER THE WHAT IF OF THE MAIN CHARACTERS
IF ONLY HE/SHE WOULD HAVE OR COULD  HAVE
I WAS PLEASANTLY SURPRISED AT THE QUALITY OF THIS MOVIE
VERY GOOD AND ENTERTAINING
YOU NEED TO OWN THIS FILM!!!! It will shock you, a very well put together film everyone must see, the bible like you never saw it in 2013!!!
